# Generate Comprehensive Project Description

Generate a comprehensive project description (500-1000 words) based on the summary provided.

## Requirements
- Length: 500-1000 words
- Include detailed sections on:
  - Product/Service explanation
  - Technology stack and architecture
  - Market opportunity and TAM
  - Competitive advantages and differentiators
  - Business model and revenue streams
  - Team capabilities and expertise
  - Growth potential and scalability

## Writing Style
- Professional prose suitable for due diligence documentation
- Use clear section headers
- Include specific data points and metrics where available
- Maintain analytical and objective tone

## Output Format
Write the description directly using markdown formatting with appropriate headers and sections.
